@startuml Personal_Recipe_Management
title Use Case Diagram: Personal Recipe Management (UC3)

skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam actorStyle awesome
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor white

left to right direction

actor "User" as User #4ECDC4

rectangle "Personal Recipe Management System" {
  usecase "UCS03-1\nCreate Recipe" as UC1 #FFE4B5
  usecase "UCS03-2\nView My Recipes" as UC2 #E0F0FF
  usecase "UCS03-3\nUpdate My Recipe" as UC3 #FFE4B5
  usecase "UCS03-4\nDelete My Recipe" as UC4 #E0F0FF
}

User --> UC1
User --> UC2
User --> UC3
User --> UC4

' Relationships
UC3 ..> UC2 : <<include>>
UC4 ..> UC2 : <<include>>
UC1 ..> UC2 : <<extend>>

note right of UC1
  Create in "Pending" status
  Full form: name, description, image,
  category, time, difficulty, ingredients, steps
  Import from AI generation
  Clone from other recipes
  10 recipes/day limit
end note

note right of UC2
  View all my recipes
  Filter by status:
  - Pending
  - Approved
  - Rejected
  Search and filter
  Statistics overview
end note

note right of UC3
  Edit when status is:
  - Pending
  - Rejected
  - Draft
  Rejected → Pending
  Keep original layout
  Same as create form
end note

note right of UC4
  Simple confirmation for pending
  Special confirmation (type name)
  for high-interaction recipes
  Show impact warning
end note

note bottom of UC2
  Recipe Status Workflow:
  Draft → Pending → Approved/Rejected
end note

@enduml




